com.mapquest.android.maps
Class RotatableIconOverlay

java.lang.Object
  com.mapquest.android.maps.Overlay
      com.mapquest.android.maps.RotatableIconOverlay

public class RotatableIconOverlay
extends Overlay

An Overlay that display a Drawable resource on the map at a point and can be rotated. Note this must not be confused with DrawableOverlay. DrawableOverlay overlays the Drawable resource at a specified bounding box and scales automatically based on the map zoom level.
